How to work and update project:

1. work on local doing npm start and nodemon server.js
2. after changes are made, git add, commit, push to master, then push to heroku from master
3. npm run build
4. drag build folder to the netlify project

if you need to update database, use heroku db cli to update the database.
you can use knex to set up base files to populate ur db




